### HU-FASE2-062 — Crear glosa (flujo exitoso)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": 4,
  "payerOfficeNumber": "OF-2026-00123",
  "officeDate": "2026-04-20",
  "notificationDate": "2026-04-22",
  "totalGlossedValue": 45000.00,
  "officeUrl": "https://soportes.empresa.local/oficios/of-2026-00123.pdf",
  "observations": "Glosa parcial por soportes incompletos."
}

