### HU-FASE2-062 — Listar glosas paginado
POST {{base}}/list
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "page": 0,
  "rows": 10,
  "search": "",
  "order_by": "g.fecha_notificacion",
  "order": "DESC"
}

