### HU-FASE2-062 — Validación negativa: factura inexistente
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": 4,
  "payerOfficeNumber": "OF-NULA",
  "officeDate": "2026-04-20",
  "notificationDate": "2026-04-22",
  "totalGlossedValue": 45000.00
}

###

### HU-FASE2-062 — Validación negativa: factura no radicada (estado inválido)
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": {{facturaId}},
  "payerOfficeNumber": "OF-2026-00124",
  "officeDate": "2026-04-20",
  "notificationDate": "2026-04-22",
  "totalGlossedValue": 1000.00
}

###

### HU-FASE2-062 — Validación negativa: valor glosado supera total de factura
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": {{facturaId}},
  "payerOfficeNumber": "OF-2026-00125",
  "officeDate": "2026-04-20",
  "notificationDate": "2026-04-22",
  "totalGlossedValue": 999999999.00
}

###

### HU-FASE2-062 — Validación negativa: campos obligatorios vacíos
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": null,
  "payerOfficeNumber": "",
  "officeDate": null,
  "notificationDate": null,
  "totalGlossedValue": 0
}

###

### HU-FASE2-062 — Validación negativa: fecha de oficio posterior a notificación
POST {{base}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "invoiceId": {{facturaId}},
  "payerOfficeNumber": "OF-2026-00126",
  "officeDate": "2026-04-25",
  "notificationDate": "2026-04-22",
  "totalGlossedValue": 1000.00
}

